text: Eadward kingc gret Alfwold biscop & Harold eorl & Alfred scyrgereuan & ealle mine þegenes on Dorsætan freondlice.
& ic ciþe eow þæt Urk min huskarl habbe his strand eall forn egen hys age land ouer eall wel & <freolslice> upp of sæ & ut on sæ & eall þæt to hys strande gedryuen hys be minum fullan bebode.
